Title: Registration, Sixth International Python Conference
Author: ipc6@python.org

<H1>Registration</H1>

<P>You can now register for the <A href="">Python Conference</A>
on-line.  Use the <A href="regform.html"><b>registration form</b></A>.

<H2>Don't Wait Till The Last Moment!</H2>

<P>The early bird registration is over - unfortunately, if you haven't
paid yet, you must pay the higher price.  The on-line registration
closes at noon, EST, October 8; <b>after that, we require on-site
registration</b>.  Payments will be accepted until 5 PM, EST, October 8;
after that, we require on-site payment.

<P>You must make your own hotel reservations.  The <A
href="accomodations.html">conference hotel</A> is booked full, and so
are some popular hotels in the area, but there are still rooms
elsewhere in San Jose.  <b>October is peak season - make your hotel
reservation as soon as possible!</b>


