<H2>Payment Options</H2>

<P>You can pay by check drawn on a US bank, or by credit card (Visa,
Mastercard, American Express, Diners Club).  Cash payments can only be
taken on site, and will incur the late fee (except for full-time
students without a credit card or US bank account).

<P>Because we are not set up with a secure Internet connection yet, we
don't take your credit card number on-line.  Instead, you can print
out the confirmation email you receive and fax or snail-mail it to us
with the desired information.  (We are sharing registration resources
with the IETF meetings, also organized by CNRI.  When they support
on-line payment, we will!)


